[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "暗くなってきたけど……もう夜？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01640",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "私の腹時計はまだ昼だって言ってるけど",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01641",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "黒い雷雲が空を覆っているんだよ。\n今まで以上に雷が落ちてきそうだね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01642",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "えっ……ちょ、ちょっと待ってください！\nなんか飛んで来ますよ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01643",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "ようやく来たな。お揃いか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01644",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "気を付けろ、来るぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_01645",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "そう急くな、せっかくだから俺の話を聞け。\nこの魔物はな、旅先の霊峰で見つけたんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01646",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "危険な大怪鳥だから本当は管理されるべきなんだが、\n今回の趣向に合わせて役立ってもらうことにした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01647",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "こいつが吐く息をくらうとだな、\nなんと身体が石になってしまう。面白いだろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01648",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "まったく面白くないよ！　戦うんじゃなかったの！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_036_01649",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "戦いさ。こういうのも戦いの中に含まれてるだろ。\n雷の対策で頭がいっぱいだったかな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01650",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "わざわざ手のうちを明かすなんて、\n随分と余裕ね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01651",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "いやいや、悠長にしているそちらこそ\n余裕があると言わざるを得んな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01652",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "空が……雲が落ちてきます！\nな、なにこれ……！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01653",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "もしかして、これ、雲じゃなくて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01654",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "イェルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Jelka",
		"model_path_hash": "7989768780593008340",
		"text": "やられた……！　大怪鳥の息を雲に混ぜて\nすでに吐いておいたとは……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_153_036_01655",
		"still_path_hash": "8715905000688515801",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "足が……動きませんわ！\nこのままでは、全身に回って……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_036_01656",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "みんな……！　私は、大丈夫？\nあとは、イェルカとシトリン！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01657",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "僕らはホムンクルスだからね……\nつまり、あの鳥を倒すのは僕らの役割ってこと",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01658",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "それを俺が黙って見ているとでも？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01659",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "シトリン",
		"romanized_name": "Citrine",
		"model_path_hash": "6017129171503572683",
		"text": "くっ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_154_036_01660",
		"still_path_hash": "924100309011770274",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "人間たちよ、パルメ族の……ひいてはこのヘルトの\n言葉に従うと誓えば助けてやろう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01661",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "ちょっと、やり方が卑怯よ！　陰湿よ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01662",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "知的と言ってほしいな。まあ、この趣向が分からぬのは\nゼロも一緒だからな。だから別行動にさせたのだが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01663",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "あいつは戦いの風情も駆け引きもなく、\nただ暴れたいだけだからな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01664",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ジェロン",
		"romanized_name": "Geron",
		"model_path_hash": "9151749121035711876",
		"text": "ぐ……！　動け、俺の身体……！\nまだ、レスナへ恩を返せていない……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_003_036_01665",
		"still_path_hash": "8725176872512870759",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "そうこうしている間に石化は進むぞ？\nさあ、早く命乞いを始めろ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01666",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "俺は、その心を折れればそれでいいんだ。\nそら、言えよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01667",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ティム",
		"romanized_name": "Tim",
		"model_path_hash": "9091556145679123684",
		"text": "い、嫌だ……！　怖い、けど……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_604_036_01668",
		"still_path_hash": "6387934691877097610",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "邪知暴虐の振る舞いには、屈しません！！\nたとえ、この身が石になっても！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01669",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "ヴァレリア、お願い。\n信じてる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_036_01670",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "……！\nええ、任せてっ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01671",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ヴァレリア",
		"romanized_name": "Valeria",
		"model_path_hash": "8455227271865371244",
		"text": "レスナーーーッ！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_002_036_01672",
		"still_path_hash": "6891392099494261238",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヘルト",
		"romanized_name": "Held",
		"model_path_hash": "1300312624310610838",
		"text": "フッ……フフッ！！！\nハーッハッハッハ！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_227_036_01673",
		"still_path_hash": "8474576122523799073",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]